      "comment": "ASTON SPRITZ (3) hit the ground running off the inside draw with a fast early sectional but run over late and missed the frame when a 1.4 lengths fourth (24.88) over 435m at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. SHAUN LEE ROSE (8) was well fancied but drifted back before winding up with a late dash home to place, 3.5 lengths from the winner (24.91) at this track in Grade 5. The form from his last run stacks up well. Leading chance. PAW JUDD (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (22.73) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Shapes as one to consider. PAW CALLIE (2) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
